basic(基础) matching(匹配)
a basic(基础) selector(选择器) specifies(详细说明) one or more scope(作用域) names, and is matched(匹配) against a token(令牌)‘s scope(作用域) names starting with the left-most(最左) scope(作用域). for a selector(选择器) to match(匹配) a token(令牌)‘s scope(作用域) name, all of its labels(标签) must be present(出现) in the same order(顺序). 





